  "slug": "better-crafting",
  "title": "Better Crafting",
  "description": "Changes and adds a few crafting recipes to make the game better",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/wishful-recipes\"><img src=\"https://images2.imgbox.com/91/a0/caG03Acz_o.png\" alt=\"This mod has been made part of Wishful Recipes. Please check it out by clicking on this. It can dynamically generate recipes on its own, meaning it is highly compatible with other mods and requires less configuration. \"/></a>\n<h1><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tCzyIk8.png\" alt=\"Title\"/></h1>\n<center><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong> \n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/2CUh6gMuCt\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/1027252425960198165?color=5b6ee1&amp;label=Discord&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Discord\" /></a> \n<a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/mars_\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/ko--fi-donate-FF5E5B?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=ko-fi&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"Support me on ko-fi\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/craft-better\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/curseforge/dt/483633?color=F16436&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=Curseforge&amp;style=for-the-badge\" alt=\"CurseForge\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/better-crafting\" ><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/modrinth/dt/better-crafting?style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white&amp;label=modrinth&amp;color=00AF5C\" alt=\"Modrinth\" /></a>\n</strong></h5></center>\n<center><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This mod changes and adds a few crafting recipes to be more balanced and practical.</p></center>\n<p><strong>Slabs to blocks</strong> - reuse slabs you no longer need<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/craft-slabs-back-into-blocks\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AJNcAtK.png\" width=\"279\" height=\"152\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Smelting sand in blast furnaces</strong> - smelting Sand and Red Sand into Glass in Blast Furnace<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/smelting-sand-in-blast-furnace\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/aqTJhBa.png\" width=\"218\" height=\"160\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Cooked Carrots</strong> - Normal Carrots, but you eat them twice as fast<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/cooked-carrots\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/6fhdFom.png\" width=\"285\" height=\"118\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Craft 6 stairs instead of 4</strong> - crafting stairs in a crafting table will yield the same amount of stairs as if you were using a stonecutter<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/craft-6-stairs-not-4\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/CuHq65H.png\" width=\"284\" height=\"158\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Use Blackstone and Endstone to craft stone tools</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/jSFGp4x.png\" width=\"263\" height=\"144\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Nether Wart Blocks to Nether Warts</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/nether-wart-block-to-nether-warts\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8XbNbev.png\" width=\"229\" height=\"127\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Blasting Netherrack into Nether Bricks</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blasting-netherrack-into-nether-bricks\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/PvwfdMc.png\" width=\"229\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Blasting Raw Metal Blocks into Blocks</strong> - smelt Raw Iron, Copper and Gold blocks in a Blast Furnace<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blasting-raw-metal-blocks-into-blocks-fabric-forge\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/addJ4gp.png\" width=\"229\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Blasting Clay</strong> - smelt Clay Blocks into Terracotta Blocks and Clay Balls into Bricks in a Blast Furnace<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/blasting-clay-and-clay-balls\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MaKUfMq.png\" width=\"229\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>Blasting Cobblestone </strong> - smelt Cobblestone into Stone and Cobbled Deepslate into Deepslate in a Blast Furnace<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/smelting-cobblestone-in-blast-a-furnace-fabric\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/q3AZgu2.png\" width=\"229\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://mars-the-planet.github.io/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/a1a13adf-7c67-48f1-8d6e-e08334434df1.png\"/></a></p>\n",
